org.apache.drill.metastore.iceberg.operate

Class IcebergRead<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.metastore.iceberg.operate.IcebergRead<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Metastore component unit type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Read<T>

    public class IcebergRead<T>
extends Object
implements Read<T>
    Implementation of Read interface. Reads information from Iceberg table based on given filter expression. Supports reading information for specific columns.

        public Read<T> columns(List<String> columns)
        Description copied from interface: Read
        Provides list of columns to be read from Metastore component. If no columns are indicated, all columns will be read. Depending on Metastore component implementation, providing list of columns to be read, can improve retrieval performance.
